sequenceDiagram
    participant C as React Client
    participant LB as Load Balancer
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant APP as Spring Boot
    participant CACHE as Redis Cache
    participant DB as MySQL Primary
    participant Q as Redis Queue
    participant W as Worker
    participant AI as OpenAI API

    Note over C,AI: Synchronous Request Flow - NL to SQL

    C->>LB: POST /api/v1/queries/nl-to-sql
    LB->>GW: Forward request
    GW->>GW: Validate JWT + Rate limit
    GW->>APP: Route to NL Query Module

    APP->>CACHE: Check schema cache
    alt Cache Hit
        CACHE-->>APP: Return cached schema
    else Cache Miss
        APP->>DB: Fetch schema metadata
        DB-->>APP: Schema data
        APP->>CACHE: Store with TTL 1hr
    end

    APP->>CACHE: Check query cache by hash
    alt Exact Query Cached
        CACHE-->>APP: Return cached result
        APP-->>C: 200 OK with result
    else Not Cached
        APP->>AI: Send schema + NL prompt
        AI-->>APP: Generated SQL
        APP->>DB: Log query + usage
        APP->>CACHE: Cache result TTL 15min
        APP-->>C: 200 OK with SQL + preview
    end

    Note over C,AI: Async Job Flow - Schema Extraction

    C->>APP: POST /api/v1/data-sources/sync
    APP->>DB: Create job record
    APP->>Q: Enqueue SCHEMA_EXTRACT job
    APP-->>C: 202 Accepted with job ID

    Q->>W: Dequeue job
    W->>W: Connect to external DB
    W->>W: Extract tables + columns + FKs
    W->>DB: Store schema snapshot
    W->>Q: Enqueue DATA_QUALITY job
    W->>DB: Update job status COMPLETED

    C->>APP: GET /api/v1/jobs/job-id/status
    APP->>DB: Check job status
    APP-->>C: 200 OK status COMPLETED

    Note over C,AI: Async Job Flow - AI Insight Generation

    Q->>W: Dequeue INSIGHT_GEN job
    W->>DB: Load schema + quality metrics
    W->>W: Chunk schema if over 100 tables
    W->>AI: Send chunk 1 with analysis prompt
    AI-->>W: Partial insights
    W->>AI: Send chunk 2 with context
    AI-->>W: More insights
    W->>DB: Store insights + usage tracking
    W->>DB: Update job status COMPLETED
